poll pop.mail.yahoo.com with proto POP3
    user "jamescaseyphd@yahoo.com" there is "james" here
    mda "/usr/bin/procmail -d %T"
    options
    no keep
    ssl
    sslcertck
    sslcertpath /etc/ssl/certs

